tip.text: Great waffles and coffee. Spacious place with plenty of seating.
Great value for money chirashi don!
Their gula Melaka jelly is awesome. Melts in your mouth and it ain't too sweet till you can only eat one or two mouths. Their beers here is 1-for-1 after 6pm too!
Beef rendang is sedap! The brioche bread goes damn well with the savoury gravy
Love their bacon mushroom melt. Bread is soft and the taste is light with a balanced taste of mushroom bacon and bread. Coffee is good too
Try their sunny side up eggs with char Siew rice! Available only from 11am onwards
A bit of a hassle in that you have to make Reservations beforehand with payment done online or bank transfer. But it's all worth it as you can then fully enjoy the hi-tea exp in the small setting
Coffee is good and their cheesecake too!
Egg tart is the flaky pastry type which i feel is better than the Honolulu cafe. Their chicken pie is not bad too.
Good coffee. Their lemon is not bad too
Very good ice cream!
Waffle is light and crispy which goes well with the heavy toppings or savory fillings
